          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p> <strong>War Powers Amendments of 2017</strong> </p> <p> This joint resolution rewrites the War Powers Resolution. </p> <p> Congressional consultation procedures are included concerning the participation of U.S. Armed Forces in certain military operations of the United Nations. </p> <p> Additional conditions are provided concerning emergency use of the Armed Forces.</p>]]></text>
